title: Match of the Day 2 - 17th May 2015 - hdtv x264
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day 2
On: BBC 1 HD  
Date: Sunday 17th May 2015 
Time: 22:30 to 23:35 

Mark Chapman introduces highlights from the day's two Premier League fixtures. The early match sees Swansea welcome Manchester City to the Liberty Stadium. The Swans have enjoyed a good first full season under manager Garry Monk and will want to end it strongly against Manuel Pellegrini's City side, whose form has tailed off badly after Christmas. It took Manchester United a while to adapt to new manager Louis van Gaal's methods, but since Christmas they have enjoyed an excellent run of form. Arsenal are the day's visitors to Old Trafford, a ground at which they beat the Red Devils in the FA Cup in March thanks to a goal from former United striker Danny Welbeck. There is also a chance to see all the goals from Saturday's top-flight games.
